<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Enrollment Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .course-info {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Course Enrollment Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>You're now enrolled in {{courseTitle}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{recipientName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Great news! Your enrollment in <strong>{{courseTitle}}</strong> has been confirmed. You now have access to all course materials and can start learning immediately.</p>
        
        <div class="course-info">
            <h3>Course Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Course:</strong> {{courseTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Instructor:</strong> {{instructorName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{courseDuration}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Here's what you can do next:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Access course materials and lessons</li>
            <li>Complete assignments and quizzes</li>
            <li>Participate in course discussions</li>
            <li>Track your learning progress</li>
            <li>Connect with your instructor and fellow students</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Ready to start learning? Click the button below to access your course:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{baseUrl}}{{actionUrl}}" class="button">{{actionText}}</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions about the course or need technical support, please don't hesitate to reach out to your instructor or our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Happy learning!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The GNAT South Tongu LMS Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email confirms your enrollment in {{courseTitle}}.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
